<li><a href="http://www.macs.hw.ac.uk/~alison/ai3notes/subsection2_4_4_1.html" class="external text" title="http://www.macs.hw.ac.uk/~alison/ai3notes/subsection2_4_4_1.html" rel="nofollow">Forward chaining systems</a></li>
